Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.50,0:00:03.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看一看誰又拿到了媽媽寄去波特蘭\N{\fs38}Well, look who got another one of Mom's care packages
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.55,0:00:05.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的關懷禮包\N{\fs38}forwarded from Portland.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.40,0:00:07.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你打算什么時候告訴他們 你并不住在波特蘭\N{\fs38}When are you going to tell them that you don't live in Portland?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.49,0:00:09.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等她不再對我指手畫腳的時候\N{\fs38}When she learns to stop criticizing me,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.42,0:00:10.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概 就是她死后吧\N{\fs38}so I guess when she's dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.75,0:00:13.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幾年前\N{\fs38}A few years back, I was
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.12,0:00:15.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我打算和我男朋友一起搬去波特蘭\N{\fs38}planning to move to Portland with a boyfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.05,0:00:17.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽說我們到那 用不了多久就會分手\N{\fs38}Mom said we'd break up as soon as we got there.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.53,0:00:20.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她錯了 動身之前我們就分了\N{\fs38}Wrong. We broke up before we left.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.06,0:00:21.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之 形勢所迫 \N{\fs38}Anyway, lemons to lemonade,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.98,0:00:23.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我認為最好的辦法就是\N{\fs38}I thought the best thing to do was
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.59,0:00:28.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓媽媽認為我已經搬到千里之外去了\N{\fs38}to let Mom think I'd moved 3,000 miles away.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.40,0:00:31.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 她很怕坐飛機  - Leigh 你知道我愛你\N{\fs38}- She's a nervous flyer. - Leigh, you know I love you,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.35,0:00:34.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我就是不懂你和Beth的矛盾\N{\fs38}but I just don't understand your problem with Beth.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.08,0:00:35.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 她那么友善貼心  - 對你而已\N{\fs38}- She's such a sweetheart. - To you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.66,0:00:37.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你嫁給了她最愛的孩子\N{\fs38}You're married to her favorite.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.28,0:00:38.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在你們的婚禮上 她說\N{\fs38}You know, at your wedding she said,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.72,0:00:40.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"我一直想要一個女兒"\N{\fs38}"I've always wanted a daughter."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.20,0:00:42.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我發誓她說的是"想要多一個女兒"\N{\fs38}No, I could've sworn she said "Another daughter."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.82,0:00:46.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在她說我是"她的公主"之后 不過你得到了關懷禮包啊\N{\fs38}After she called me her prince. But you got a care package.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.26,0:00:49.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這才不是什么關懷禮包 滿滿的都是鄙夷\N{\fs38}This isn't a care package. It's a box of criticism...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.56,0:00:52.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,節食書 我太胖了 面霜 我皺紋多\N{\fs38}Diet book, I'm fat. Face cream, I'm wrinkly.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.02,0:00:55.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每日一詞日歷 雙重侮辱\N{\fs38}Word-a-day calendar, double insult,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.62,0:00:57.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我詞匯量少且弄不清日子\N{\fs38}I don't know words or what day it is...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.30,0:00:58.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些都送你們了\N{\fs38}You guys can have this stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.54,0:01:00.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 我一點也不想要  - 餅干我要了\N{\fs38}- I don't want any of it. - I'm taking the cookies!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.72,0:01:02.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是帶軟糖的餅干嗎\N{\fs38}Are those the ones with the fudge?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.26,0:01:03.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等她來過感恩節的時候\N{\fs38}Well, maybe she'll bring you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.00,0:01:06.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許會給你帶些別的東西\N{\fs38}some more when she's here for Thanksgiving.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.47,0:01:09.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們要來這里過感恩節 不一直是你們過去嗎\N{\fs38}They're coming here for Thanksgiving? You guys always go there!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.50,0:01:11.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 如果我撞見他們了怎么辦  - 我有一個瘋狂的想法\N{\fs38}- What if I run into them? - Here's a crazy notion...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.67,0:01:14.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像正常人那樣和他們說說話怎么樣\N{\fs38}speak to them like a normal person.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.24,0:01:17.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許我可以馬上買張到巴巴多斯的機票\N{\fs38}Or maybe I could get a last-minute ticket to Barbados.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.24,0:01:17.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fs36}拉丁美洲某國
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.72,0:01:20.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 我下個建議就是這個了  - 嗨 各位\N{\fs38}- That was my next suggestion. - Hey, guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.52,0:01:22.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實沒什么大不了的事\N{\fs38}It's not a thing or anything,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.42,0:01:25.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我看見Graham得到了些餅干\N{\fs38}but I saw that Graham got some cookies...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.06,0:01:27.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是有一點點好奇\N{\fs38}I was just curious as to, like...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.92,0:01:32.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 為什么  - 因為他還小 而你已經19歲了\N{\fs38}- why. - Because he's a kid and you're 19.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.88,0:01:35.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事 好吧 我理解\N{\fs38}Totally cool. Yeah, I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.56,0:01:38.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸叫你分給我一塊\N{\fs38}Dad said I could have one!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.38,0:01:40.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為啥我們不能騙他咱搬去了波特蘭\N{\fs38}Why can't we tell him we moved to Portland?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.62,0:02:01.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這真是史上最爛感恩節了\N{\fs38}This is the worst Thanksgiving ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.14,0:02:03.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在才9點半 還沒開始呢\N{\fs38}It's 9:30. It hasn't even started yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.56,0:02:05.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我難得喜歡一個節日\N{\fs38}It's the one holiday that I love,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.38,0:02:06.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們就非得毀了它是吧\N{\fs38}and you guys are changing everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.96,0:02:08.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你什么時候喜歡去爺爺奶奶家了\N{\fs38}Since when do you like going to Grandma and Grandpa's?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.84,0:02:10.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忘了你一路的抱怨了嗎\N{\fs38}You complain the whole way down.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.68,0:02:14.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是青少年 我抱怨一件事\N{\fs38}I'm a teenager. I complain about stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.12,0:02:17.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并不表示我不喜歡 你們倆真過分\N{\fs38}It doesn't mean I don't love it. You guys are terrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.14,0:02:20.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這表示你愛我們 對嗎\N{\fs38}So that means you love us, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.04,0:02:22.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 打包完畢\N{\fs38}All right. All packed.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.80,0:02:25.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天下午 我就會在亞特蘭大\N{\fs38}By this afternoon, I'll be kicking back,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.42,0:02:28.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一身輕松地啜飲著雞尾酒了\N{\fs38}sipping daiquiris in Atlanta.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.82,0:02:31.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時間太趕了 只能買到有經停的機票了\N{\fs38}It's a last-minute ticket, guys. It's mostly layovers.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.18,0:02:33.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提醒我了 我要帶上你們的護頸枕 \N{\fs38}Ooh, that reminds me, I'm going to take your neck pillow.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.34,0:02:38.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是她的損失 這個感恩節會很棒的\N{\fs38}Well, she's missing out. It's gonna be a great Thanksgiving
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.38,0:02:40.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在你的美味火雞大餐之后\N{\fs38}with your amazing turkey, and then afterwards,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.10,0:02:41.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們去中央公園玩玩橄欖球\N{\fs38}we'll play a little football in Central Park.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.43,0:02:44.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 今年還要玩橄欖球嗎\N{\fs38}Yeah, really? You're gonna play football again this year?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.03,0:02:46.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 為什么不 我喜歡橄欖球啊  - 我知道 可是\N{\fs38}- Why not? I love football. - I know you do, it's just...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.33,0:02:47.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你爸爸逼得你太緊了\N{\fs38}your Dad pushes you too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.84,0:02:49.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Steve不明白你不比從前了\N{\fs38}Steve doesn't get that it's harder for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.48,0:02:51.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道 我還挺喜歡他這樣的\N{\fs38}Well, I don't know. I kind of love that about him.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.02,0:02:53.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不格外呵護我\N{\fs38}He doesn't treat me with kid gloves.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.86,0:02:54.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好很好 真是太好了\N{\fs38}Oh, it's great. It's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.78,0:02:56.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以他得到有趣的橄欖球小子\N{\fs38}So he gets fun football guy,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.54,0:02:59.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就得到一個事后精疲力盡的家伙\N{\fs38}and then I get exhausted guy afterwards.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.26,0:03:02.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 沒那么糟吧  - 你去年吃晚飯的時候睡著了\N{\fs38}- It's not so bad. - You fell asleep at dinner last year.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.28,0:03:05.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 火雞有催眠效果嘛  - 你根本都還沒切火雞呢\N{\fs38}- Eh, turkey makes you sleepy. - You hadn't carved it yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.32,0:03:08.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我當時低著頭 表達感恩之心\N{\fs38}I had my head bowed, giving thanks...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.46,0:03:11.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 表了20分鐘  - 嗯哼\N{\fs38}- for 20 minutes. - Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.72,0:03:15.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 不玩橄欖球 你肯定希望我\N{\fs38}Okay, no football. Anyway, you'll want me awake
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.24,0:03:17.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感恩節"小活動"時醒著吧\N{\fs38}for the post-thanksgiving festivities.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.88,0:03:20.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帶著一肚子的肉汁嗎 做夢吧\N{\fs38}With a belly full of gravy? Dream on.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.40,0:03:22.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我夢著呢\N{\fs38}I'm dreaming.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.04,0:03:26.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 爸媽 你們來得這么快  - 火雞節快樂\N{\fs38}- Mom, Dad, you've got here quick! - Happy turkey day!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.94,0:03:29.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咯咯 咯咯 我的填充物在哪呢\N{\fs38}Gobble, gobble, gobble! I want that stuffing!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.82,0:03:31.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 爸爸 你抱得太緊了\N{\fs38}Okay, okay, Dad. You're squeezing me too tight.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.04,0:03:33.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 我要斷氣了  - 嗨 兩位\N{\fs38}- I'm blacking out. - Hi, guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.82,0:03:34.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗨 親愛的\N{\fs38}Hi, honey!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.82,0:03:36.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 給我點那個\N{\fs38}Some of that, give me some of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.60,0:03:38.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,親愛的 真高興見到你\N{\fs38}Oh, honey. So great to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.52,0:03:40.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 我愛你 我愛你們  - 你們可真早\N{\fs38}- I love you. I love you. - You guys are early.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.62,0:03:45.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 早了差不多六個小時  - 我們想避開交通高峰期\N{\fs38}- Like, six hours early. - Well, we wanted to beat the traffic.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.06,0:03:48.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 避開了高峰期 知道我們還避開了什么嗎 太陽\N{\fs38}Yep, we beat the traffic. You know what else we beat? The sun.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.46,0:03:51.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們一上路 發現路上幾乎沒人\N{\fs38}Well, you know, we got on the road, there's nobody on the road.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.73,0:03:53.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在某個時間段出發的話\N{\fs38}You get on the road a certain amount of time,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.14,0:03:54.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就不會有很多人\N{\fs38}there's nobody...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.54,0:03:59.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- Leigh  - 嗨 我剛進門\N{\fs38}- Leigh? - Hey, I was just coming in the door...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.18,0:04:03.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 想給你們一個驚喜  - 寶貝 真是大大的驚喜\N{\fs38}- to surprise you. - Hi, honey. What a nice surprise.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.94,0:04:05.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 見到你太好了  - 噢\N{\fs38}- So great to see you. - Aw!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.04,0:04:07.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看起來真漂亮 我愛你\N{\fs38}You look so beautiful. Oh, I love you, I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.94,0:04:10.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你從波特蘭一路飛過來的\N{\fs38}You flew all the way here from Portland?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.70,0:04:14.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 所以才有這些大包小包\N{\fs38}I did, which is why I have all these bags.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.62,0:04:16.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這樣的\N{\fs38}That certainly explains that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.99,0:04:21.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- Leigh 好久不見了  - 你一點都沒變\N{\fs38}- Leigh, it's so great to see you. - You haven't changed a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.72,0:04:24.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寶貝 你一路經停了多少次\N{\fs38}Sweetie, how many layovers did you have?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.38,0:04:26.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起來這么疲憊\N{\fs38}Because you look a little tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.36,0:04:28.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但愿你沒買空中百貨雜志上的東西\N{\fs38}I hope you didn't buy anything from that Skymall magazine.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.80,0:04:29.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我買過一個石頭\N{\fs38}'Cause I bought a rock
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.96,0:04:31.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用來藏我的鑰匙\N{\fs38}from this thing once to hide my keys under.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.08,0:04:35.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在我找不到該死的鑰匙了 Mikey 接住包\N{\fs38}Now I can't find my damn keys. Mikey, help me with this bag.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.04,0:04:39.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 親愛的\N{\fs38}Excuse me, honey.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.30,0:04:40.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 抱歉  - 跟上啊 Mikey\N{\fs38}- Sorry. - Try to keep up, Mikey.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.50,0:04:45.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Leigh 寶貝 十一月來紐約\N{\fs38}Leigh, sweetie, this is what you pack
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.32,0:04:47.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就帶了這些東西 還比基尼\N{\fs38}for New York in November? A bikini?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.38,0:04:50.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么說呢 我就是樂觀\N{\fs38}What can I say? I'm an optimist.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.19,0:04:54.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 在經歷了這么多事之后 你真行\N{\fs38}Really? Even after everything? Good for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.02,0:04:58.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看看 都皺巴巴的 我來疊好吧\N{\fs38}Oh, look at this. Everything's wrinkled. I'll fold it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.24,0:05:01.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 什么 噓  - 你看她說的\N{\fs38}- What? Shh. - Can you believe her?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.73,0:05:04.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看著疲憊 我衣服疊得不好 我不檢點\N{\fs38}I look tired, my folding's not good, I'm a slut.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.23,0:05:05.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 她沒這么說啊  - 馬上要了\N{\fs38}- She didn't say that! - She will.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.96,0:05:08.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我包里有些東西會給人這種感覺\N{\fs38}There's some stuff in my bag that paints a picture.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.17,0:05:09.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Leigh 你媽媽只是在\N{\fs38}Leigh, your Mom is just
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.42,0:05:11.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 關心你而已  - 你說得輕松\N{\fs38}- trying to be nice. - Easy for you to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.90,0:05:14.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒有被她的幫助激光瞄準\N{\fs38}You're not in the crosshairs of her laser beam of help.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.64,0:05:16.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是我 我會很感激的\N{\fs38}Well, if I were, I'd be grateful.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.82,0:05:19.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得幫助激光聽著挺不錯的\N{\fs38}I think a laser beam of help sounds kind of nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.35,0:05:22.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 我把你的衣服整好了\N{\fs38}Okay, I straightened out your clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.74,0:05:25.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起來 你打算在紐約好好享受啊\N{\fs38}Looks like you're planning on having a good time in New York.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.16,0:05:27.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又來了\N{\fs38}And there it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.55,0:05:31.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 媽媽\N{\fs38}You know, Mom,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.09,0:05:34.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Annie剛才和我說 \N{\fs38}Annie was just telling me how much she would love
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.04,0:05:36.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她很希望你幫她準備今晚的晚餐\N{\fs38}to have your help making dinner tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.98,0:05:39.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 你是這么說的嗎  - 沒錯 就是這樣\N{\fs38}- Weren't you just saying that to me? - Yes! Yes, I was.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.92,0:05:41.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不像某些人\N{\fs38}Unlike some other people,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.06,0:05:43.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很樂意別人幫我 Beth\N{\fs38}I appreciate a little bit of help, Beth.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.52,0:05:46.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我們先好好整整這廚房吧\N{\fs38}Let's start by whipping this kitchen into shape.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.96,0:05:48.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,臟廚房可燒不出好飯菜\N{\fs38}You can't cook in a filthy kitchen.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.21,0:05:54.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 臟  - 好好享受吧\N{\fs38}- Uh... filthy? - Enjoy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.12,0:05:59.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在嗎 爸爸 你還記得帶橄欖球呢\N{\fs38}You in here, Dad? Oh, you remembered the football.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.20,0:06:01.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好\N{\fs38}That's good. Ugh...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.14,0:06:02.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還帶了兩個就有點奇怪了\N{\fs38}You brought two. That's just weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.92,0:06:04.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,準備好出去打球了嗎\N{\fs38}So you ready to get out there and play?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.86,0:06:06.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關于這個 爸爸 既然都來這兒了\N{\fs38}About that, Dad, we're in the city this year.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.90,0:06:08.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什么不找些別的有趣的事呢\N{\fs38}Why don't we find some other fun stuff to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.76,0:06:12.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么 去做指甲嗎 還是買女性胸罩\N{\fs38}What, like get our nails done, try on some woman bras?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.36,0:06:14.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"女性胸罩" 胸罩還有男性的嗎\N{\fs38}"Woman bras"? "Bra" Doesn't cover it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.32,0:06:16.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 你把球帶來了\N{\fs38}Sweet! You got the pigskin out!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.98,0:06:17.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們還打不打球了\N{\fs38}Are we gonna go do this or what?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.87,0:06:19.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 你什么時候喜歡上橄欖球了  - 你開玩笑嗎\N{\fs38}- Since when do you like football? - Are you kidding me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.91,0:06:20.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可愛了\N{\fs38}I love this game.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.94,0:06:24.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我恨它 每一年都受盡嘲笑\N{\fs38}I hate this game. Every year I totally humiliate myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.60,0:06:27.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過今年不會了 我發現了一個網站\N{\fs38}Not this time. I found a how-to site online,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.46,0:06:29.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,教你怎么投出一個完美的螺旋球\N{\fs38}which taught me how to throw a perfect spiral.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.18,0:06:34.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像 T-bow一樣\N{\fs38}Just like... I want to say T-bow.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.86,0:06:37.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是投球的那個嗎\N{\fs38}Is he the thrower guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.84,0:06:41.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ian 也許你能幫個忙 \N{\fs38}Ian, maybe you can help. Your Mom is trying to weasel out
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.24,0:06:42.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你媽媽不想和我一起打球\N{\fs38}of playing football with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.62,0:06:43.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她一天都得在廚房轉悠\N{\fs38}Oh, well, she has to cook all day.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.04,0:06:46.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 兒子 他是說我  -  真妙\N{\fs38}- He means me, son. - Oh. Good one.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.66,0:06:48.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這大城市 哪里有合適的場地啊\N{\fs38}Where's a good place to play in this big city?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.43,0:06:51.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很明顯爸爸真的很想玩橄欖球\N{\fs38}It was clear Dad really wanted to play football.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.80,0:06:54.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以很難拒絕他的要求\N{\fs38}It was gonna be hard to say "No" To him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.48,0:06:56.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中央公園 中央公園不錯\N{\fs38}Central Park. Central Park's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.52,0:06:57.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我沒拒絕\N{\fs38}so I didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.46,0:07:04.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寶貝兒 波特蘭怎樣啊\N{\fs38}So, honey, how is Portland?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.56,0:07:08.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,波特蘭 波特蘭嘛\N{\fs38}Portland? Well, Portland...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.70,0:07:12.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,霧靄沉沉形似"波" 聚起于港勢其"特" 御風而去沖"蘭"破\N{\fs38}all the mist from the ports, rolling onto the land.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.50,0:07:16.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美得令人窒息\N{\fs38}It's... breathtaking.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.12,0:07:17.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我從沒去過波特蘭\N{\fs38}I've never been to Portland.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.23,0:07:20.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在干什么呢\N{\fs38}Ooh. What are you making there?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.10,0:07:23.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我找到一份不錯的自制蔓越莓醬的食譜\N{\fs38}Oh, I found this amazing recipe for homemade cranberry sauce.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.46,0:07:26.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里面用了丁香來開胃\N{\fs38}It uses cloves for a savory note.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.38,0:07:28.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽起來挺有意思的\N{\fs38}Well, that sounds interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.54,0:07:30.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 當然  - 只是\N{\fs38}- Yeah. - It's just that...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.32,0:07:34.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火雞已經挺開胃了的\N{\fs38}turkey is already savory.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.52,0:07:38.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們有必要在開胃菜上再加開胃菜嗎\N{\fs38}And do we really want to put savory on top of savory?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.20,0:07:44.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 要  - 肯定會很棒的\N{\fs38}- Yes? - I'm sure it'll be great.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.82,0:07:48.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們還有罐頭備用嗎\N{\fs38}Do we have any of the canned stuff as backup?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.74,0:07:51.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 感覺還不錯嗎  - 她的確有些分寸問題\N{\fs38}- Having fun yet? - Okay, so she has some boundary issues,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.92,0:07:54.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我還應付的了\N{\fs38}but this isn't anything that I can't handle.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.40,0:07:56.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Beth 我們不需要備用\N{\fs38}Uh, Beth, we don't have need backup
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.84,0:07:58.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我的美味晚餐計劃里\N{\fs38}because I planned a delicious meal
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.66,0:08:01.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用不著蔓越莓醬罐頭\N{\fs38}that does not call for canned cranberry sauce.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.82,0:08:05.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說啥 我們一直用的都是蔓越莓醬罐頭啊\N{\fs38}What did you just say? We always have canned cranberry sauce.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.36,0:08:06.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別擔心 親愛的\N{\fs38}Don't worry, sweetie.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.64,0:08:09.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你媽要做種新的古怪的蔓越莓醬\N{\fs38}Your mother's making a new weird cranberry sauce,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.93,0:08:12.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來代替普通美國老百姓都喜歡的那種\N{\fs38}instead of the normal American kind everyone loves.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.96,0:08:14.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你毀了感恩節\N{\fs38}Well, you've ruined Thanksgiving.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.00,0:08:16.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好像已經毀過一次了\N{\fs38}I thought I already ruined it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.20,0:08:20.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你毀了我才開始習慣的糟糕版本的感恩節\N{\fs38}You've ruined the ruined version I was just getting used to.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.17,0:08:25.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,波特蘭的手工果醬工廠\N{\fs38}Wow. I haven't seen anyone that upset
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.42,0:08:27.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果醬大罷工之后\N{\fs38}since the big jam strike
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.16,0:08:29.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還沒見過有人這么生氣\N{\fs38}over at the Portland artisanal jam factory.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.86,0:08:34.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 稍等一下\N{\fs38}All right, just a sec.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.46,0:08:36.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無名指在二三道線之間\N{\fs38}Ring finger between laces two and three...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.42,0:08:38.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 我練習用的球上面有數字\N{\fs38}Sorry, the ball I practiced with had numbers on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.22,0:08:41.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,臀 肘 肩 扔\N{\fs38}Hips, elbow, shoulder, throw.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.86,0:08:44.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 臀 肘 肩 快速扔  - 哇\N{\fs38}- Hips, elbow, shoulder... blitz throw! - Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.72,0:08:47.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,輕點撞 我們還在練習\N{\fs38}Easy with the cheap hits! We're just rehearsing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.56,0:08:48.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸 這挺好\N{\fs38}Well, Dad, this was great.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.90,0:08:50.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什么比得上感恩節來場橄欖球\N{\fs38}Nothing like a game of football on Thanksgiving.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.92,0:08:52.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 我答應過今年我不會玩的\N{\fs38}Yes, I promised I wasn't gonna play this year.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.80,0:08:54.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是說過 我們要去\N{\fs38}And yes, I said we were gonna go
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.46,0:08:56.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逛逛紐約 看看裝飾藝術門\N{\fs38}on a walking tour of the Art Deco doors of New York,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.84,0:08:58.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 我們\N{\fs38}but you know what, we
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.62,0:09:00.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不玩的太過的話 還是挺開心的\N{\fs38}actually had a good time without overdoing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.01,0:09:02.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛剛算是個還可以的小熱身\N{\fs38}Well, that was a nice, little warm-up.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.70,0:09:04.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在我們要動真格的了\N{\fs38}Now, we're gonna go for the real game.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.34,0:09:05.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 你說啥  - 來真格的\N{\fs38}- Say what now? - The real game.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.60,0:09:07.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你耳朵不好使了嗎 Linda\N{\fs38}Something wrong with your hearing, Linda?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.35,0:09:09.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Linda 你邏輯在哪\N{\fs38}Linda? That doesn't even make any sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.38,0:09:11.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是說 女人跟聽力啥關系\N{\fs38}I mean, women don't lose their hea...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.58,0:09:13.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之 這里是紐約 爸爸\N{\fs38}Anyway, this is New York, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.22,0:09:14.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主意挺好 但是咱這不興\N{\fs38}It's a nice idea, but you don't just go up
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.56,0:09:15.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在街上抓陌生人打比賽\N{\fs38}to strangers and ask them for a pickup game.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.89,0:09:18.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 你們找人呢嗎  - 呃\N{\fs38}- You guys are looking for a game? - Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.74,0:09:20.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對啊 但是你們要小心咯 \N{\fs38}Yeah. But you better watch your back,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.73,0:09:22.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為這家伙 可是頭野獸\N{\fs38}because this guy is an animal!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.36,0:09:25.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 一頭答應他太太不會玩得太過的野獸\N{\fs38}Yeah, an animal who promised his wife he wouldn't overdo it.
