Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.90,0:09:31.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 感恩節快樂  - 快樂嗎\N{\fs38}- Happy Thanksgiving! - Is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.32,0:09:35.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 見到你總是這么開心 Eve  - 我媽的晚餐肯定糟透了\N{\fs38}- Always a pleasure, Eve. - Mom's dinner is going to suck!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.90,0:09:37.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她要自己做蔓越莓醬\N{\fs38}She's making real cranberry sauce
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.64,0:09:39.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而不是去買罐頭\N{\fs38}instead of buying the canned kind.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.38,0:09:41.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用真的蔓越莓嗎 好惡心啊\N{\fs38}With real cranberries? That's disgusting!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.32,0:09:44.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那玩意兒長在沼澤里的\N{\fs38}Those things grow in a bog.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.48,0:09:46.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罐頭形狀那種的才好呢\N{\fs38}What you need is the stuff that takes the shape of the can.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.44,0:09:47.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從罐頭里慢慢滑出\N{\fs38}You know, where it globs out all slow.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.72,0:09:49.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發出那種 聲音\N{\fs38}And it makes that... sound.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.14,0:09:51.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 罐頭鋼圈才能鎖住風味  - 我就這意思\N{\fs38}- The ridges lock in the flavor. - That's what I'm saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.52,0:09:53.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去拿外衣 我們去買罐頭\N{\fs38}Grab your coat. We going can shopping.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.40,0:10:00.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喔 太多鹽了吧\N{\fs38}Whoa! Oh, that's too much salt.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.32,0:10:01.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是少量 不是倒一把\N{\fs38}That's a pinch, not a dash.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.84,0:10:04.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許你應該做準備工作\N{\fs38}Maybe you should do prep.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.22,0:10:09.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 接受Beth的幫助\N{\fs38}Okay, so being on the receiving end of Beth's
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.68,0:10:12.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比想象中的要難\N{\fs38}help was a little rougher than I expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.64,0:10:16.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塑料的刀板啊\N{\fs38}Whoa! A plastic cutting board?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.55,0:10:19.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒聽說過BPA嗎\N{\fs38}Have you not heard of BPAs?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.55,0:10:19.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fs36}BPA 塑料產品中常含 可致癌
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.04,0:10:24.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 我去拿我的旅行刀板  - 你還打包了個刀板\N{\fs38}- I'll get my travel board. - You pack a cutting board?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.62,0:10:27.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我本想堅持我的立場\N{\fs38}I tried to stand my ground,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.38,0:10:30.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我已經有點被Beth洗腦了\N{\fs38}but Beth may have gotten in my head a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.66,0:10:36.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這鍋...要開...\N{\fs38}The... the... the pot is boi...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.94,0:10:38.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她擊潰了我\N{\fs38}Okay, she broke me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.47,0:10:40.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能攪這個土豆嗎 Beth\N{\fs38}Am I allowed to stir the potatoes, Beth?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.84,0:10:43.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs38}Beth\NBeth?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.96,0:10:46.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蔓越莓醬\N{\fs38}Cranberry sauce?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.24,0:10:48.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感恩節怎么買的到蔓越莓醬\N{\fs38}You can't buy cranberry sauce on Thanksgiving.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.28,0:10:49.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們連一個都沒有了嗎\N{\fs38}You don't even have one can?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.75,0:10:52.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Chuck 我們還有蔓越莓醬嗎\N{\fs38}Chuck! Do we have any cranberry sauce?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.46,0:10:54.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感恩節怎么買的到蔓越莓醬\N{\fs38}You can't buy cranberry sauce on Thanksgiving.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.02,0:10:57.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 我就這么說的  - 你們感恩節不賣\N{\fs38}- That's what I said! - If you're not gonna bother selling
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.56,0:11:00.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感恩節用品 你們今天干嘛還開門\N{\fs38}Thanksgiving stuff on Thanksgiving, why are you even open?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.32,0:11:02.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為有人開始采購圣誕節用品了\N{\fs38}For people who want to get a jump on their christmas shopping.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.58,0:11:04.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你告訴他們我們有很多拐杖糖了嗎\N{\fs38}Did you tell them we got plenty of candy canes?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.86,0:11:07.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我正要說 聽著 你要是在休息\N{\fs38}I was about to! Look, if you're on break,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.83,0:11:10.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就好好休息 Chuck 我們有拐杖糖\N{\fs38}then take your break, Chuck! We have candy canes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.67,0:11:11.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們換家好點的店吧\N{\fs38}Let's find a better store.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.20,0:11:13.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等到最后一刻才想起要買\N{\fs38}A lot of judgment coming from the guy
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.66,0:11:15.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蔓越莓醬的家伙意見還真多\N{\fs38}who waited until the last minute to buy cranberry sauce.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.94,0:11:19.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始 一\N{\fs38}Hut! One Mississippi.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.14,0:11:21.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,臀 肘 肩 扔\N{\fs38}Hips, elbow, shoulder, throw.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.58,0:11:23.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,臀 肘 肩 扔\N{\fs38}hips, elbow, shoulder, throw!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.10,0:11:31.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要扔到樹也好啊 我們就觸地得分了\N{\fs38}If you were throwing to the tree, we'd have a touchdown.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.16,0:11:32.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這手臂跟大炮似的啊\N{\fs38}That's quite a cannon you got.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.52,0:11:33.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過你準心還得再加強點\N{\fs38}You just gotta work on your aim a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.64,0:11:35.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 也許下次我得瞄準你媽\N{\fs38}Oh, yeah? Maybe I gotta work on your Mom's aim.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.42,0:11:37.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 啥  - 抱歉\N{\fs38}- What? - Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.46,0:11:39.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是 之前沒說過臟話\N{\fs38}I just... I've never trash-talked before.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.58,0:11:42.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺太棒了 就像你媽媽一樣\N{\fs38}It's exhilarating. Like your Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.34,0:11:44.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 不說了 我太興奮了\N{\fs38}I'm sorry, that's it. I promise. I'm just pumped up. Just...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.64,0:11:49.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啦 布置戰略 你出去五碼\N{\fs38}All right, here's the play... you go out 5 yards,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.44,0:11:51.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后轉身接球 我假投\N{\fs38}you buttonhook, I'll pump-fake,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.64,0:11:53.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你直奔底線 我給你個深傳\N{\fs38}you run a fly route to the deep post.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.94,0:11:57.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些都要今天做啊 爸 我累死了\N{\fs38}All of this is gonna happen today? Come on, Dad. I'm beat.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.44,0:11:58.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別這樣 Mikey 再加把勁\N{\fs38}Come on, Mikey. Dig deep.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.76,0:12:00.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們要給孩子做一個怎樣的榜樣啊\N{\fs38}What kind of an example are we setting for the boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.24,0:12:07.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但愿他是在和只母狗跳舞\N{\fs38}I hope that's a girl dog he's dancing with.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.42,0:12:10.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們甚至都不是同一物種\N{\fs38}Again, with the... they're not even the same species.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.80,0:12:12.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧 爸 開始吧\N{\fs38}Come on, Dad, let's do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.04,0:12:14.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 好 好\N{\fs38}Okay, okay, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.38,0:12:15.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 好\N{\fs38}Okay, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.10,0:12:17.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能叫你兒子嗎\N{\fs38}Mind if I call you stepson?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.56,0:12:19.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我要和你媽結婚了\N{\fs38}'Cause I'm about to marry your mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.13,0:12:20.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 我們彼此相愛\N{\fs38}That's right, we've fallen in love.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.74,0:12:24.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,始于肉體 現在感情日益加深\N{\fs38}It started out physical, now it's so much more.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.07,0:12:25.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我永遠都替代不了你的父親\N{\fs38}I'll never replace your Dad,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.66,0:12:28.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但不管你有什么問題盡管找我就好\N{\fs38}but you can come to me with whatever...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.74,0:12:30.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道他已經開球了吧\N{\fs38}You know he hiked the ball already, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.62,0:12:38.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 哦  - 跑 爸 跑 \N{\fs38}- Oh! - Go, Dad! Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.15,0:12:40.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跑 跑 跑 耶\N{\fs38}Go, go, go, go! Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.18,0:12:44.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們做到了 爸 你是對的 爸\N{\fs38}Yeah, we did it! You were right, Dad! Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.60,0:12:47.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒事 沒事\N{\fs38}I'm okay, I'm okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.80,0:12:49.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸 撞胸 哦 天\N{\fs38}Hey Dad, chest bump! Oh, gee.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.80,0:12:55.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 好些了嗎 爸  - 我去叫輛救護車\N{\fs38}- Feeling better, Dad? - I'm gonna call an ambulance.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.52,0:12:56.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不用了 我沒事\N{\fs38}No, no, no. I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.25,0:13:00.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是有點胸痛 偶爾都會這樣的\N{\fs38}It's a little chest pain. I get it from time to time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.52,0:13:02.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,醫生說了是心絞痛\N{\fs38}You know, the Doctor says it's angina.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.02,0:13:08.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心絞痛 拜托 你們連這都接受不了\N{\fs38}Angina... come on, you guys aren't gonna run with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.68,0:13:10.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弱爆了\N{\fs38}Come on, you guys are weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.32,0:13:11.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說真的 你確定你沒事吧 爸爸\N{\fs38}Seriously, you sure you're okay, Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.78,0:13:14.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 沒事 但是別說出去\N{\fs38}Yeah, yeah, but let's keep it between us.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.23,0:13:17.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別告訴女人們 我不想她們擔心\N{\fs38}Let's not tell the ladies. I don't want them to worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.50,0:13:19.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Graham Graham 走吧\N{\fs38}Graham, Graham! Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.90,0:13:24.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 他瘋了 不叫救護車就算了\N{\fs38}All right, he's crazy. If we're not calling an ambulance,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.16,0:13:25.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少別徒步回家吧\N{\fs38}we're at least not walking home.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.60,0:13:27.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去叫輛的士 你負責把他塞進車里\N{\fs38}I'll call a cab, and you just shove him in.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.95,0:13:30.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ian說的有道理 但我之所以能觸地得分\N{\fs38}Ian had a point, but I scored that touchdown
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.46,0:13:32.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因為我爸沒有格外呵護我\N{\fs38}because my Dad didn't treat me with kid gloves.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.84,0:13:34.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道他希望我也能這樣對他\N{\fs38}And I knew he'd want me to treat him the same way.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.58,0:13:37.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他想走回去 就走回去好了\N{\fs38}Man wants to walk, let him walk.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.82,0:13:39.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 但我能叫輛的士嗎\N{\fs38}All right, then, can I take a cab?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.38,0:13:41.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你剛不跟我撞胸慶祝那下好像把我傷著了\N{\fs38}I think I broke something when you ditched me on the chest bump.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.40,0:13:48.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,躲著老媽么\N{\fs38}Hiding out from Mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.80,0:13:54.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不 我只是在收拾垃圾房而已\N{\fs38}No, no, I was just straightening up the trash room.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.44,0:13:57.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道垃圾房這樣后我就放不下心\N{\fs38}I just can't relax until I know the trash room...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.52,0:14:01.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 她知道我在這里嗎  - 親愛的 她擊潰了你\N{\fs38}- Does she know that I'm down here? - Oh, sweetie, she broke you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.00,0:14:03.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這里現在是我家了\N{\fs38}This is my home now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.34,0:14:06.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是受不了了\N{\fs38}I just couldn't handle it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.52,0:14:10.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mike把我一個人扔在這里 去散了有史以來最長的步 \N{\fs38}Mike left me all alone, went for the longest walk in history.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.02,0:14:13.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的意思是 能有多少扇藝術裝飾門\N{\fs38}I mean, how many Art Deco doors can there be?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.22,0:14:15.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我多么想說 我早就說過\N{\fs38}I was so looking forward to saying,"I told you so,"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.76,0:14:17.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我現在只想給你個擁抱\N{\fs38}But now I just want to give you a hug.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.94,0:14:20.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在你徹底經歷這些事情以后\N{\fs38}After you've taken a thorough shower.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.22,0:14:23.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我錯了 Leigh 我現在懂了\N{\fs38}I'm so sorry, Leigh. I get it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.40,0:14:26.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隨便你假裝住在波特蘭多久都可以\N{\fs38}You can fake live in Portland for as long as you want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.94,0:14:28.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我確實喜歡那里\N{\fs38}I do love it there.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.67,0:14:32.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們開放了一條高架路給躺式自行車\N{\fs38}They're opening an elevated trail for recumbent bicycles...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.28,0:14:35.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 這個模式關不掉了  - 我知道\N{\fs38}- I can't... I can't turn it off. - I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.72,0:14:43.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 我們已經晃蕩五間商店了 什么收獲都沒有\N{\fs38}Okay, we've been to five stores, and nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.26,0:14:45.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得我們可以放棄了\N{\fs38}I guess we should just stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.80,0:14:47.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 放棄吧 我們回去了\N{\fs38}Yeah, absolutely. Let's go back.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.62,0:14:50.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 我不想放棄  - 我也是\N{\fs38}- I don't want to stop. - Me neither.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.98,0:14:52.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道剛開始只是因為蔓越莓醬\N{\fs38}I know it started out as just cranberry sauce,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.82,0:14:54.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我覺得已經演變成一種象征了\N{\fs38}but I feel like it's becoming a symbol.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.60,0:14:56.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許作為人類 我們有強烈的需求...\N{\fs38}I mean, maybe as a people, we have a greater need for...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.94,0:14:59.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 找到了  - 我勒個去 在這呢\N{\fs38}- Found some. - I'll be damned. There she is.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.14,0:15:03.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們這樣不好吧 這樣好嗎\N{\fs38}We couldn't. Could we?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.88,0:15:11.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這絕對沒問題 我們用這堆罐頭換一罐\N{\fs38}This is totally okay. We put all these cans in, take one out,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.32,0:15:12.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 道德上我們還是一清二白的  - 我同意\N{\fs38}- we're morally in the clear. - I agree.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.72,0:15:14.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 我們可以抬頭挺胸  - 是的\N{\fs38}- We can hold our heads high. - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.52,0:15:16.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過還是別讓別人看見\N{\fs38}You just make sure no one else sees us.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.74,0:15:20.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 你們在干什么\N{\fs38}Excuse me. What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.34,0:15:24.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什么的 我們先捐了一堆罐頭\N{\fs38}It's fine. We put a bunch of other cans in here first.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.64,0:15:25.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鷹嘴豆罐頭 湯罐頭\N{\fs38}Chickpeas, soup...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.98,0:15:29.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽著 這東西基本上就是糖和食用色素的混合體\N{\fs38}Listen, this stuff is mostly sugar and food coloring.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.42,0:15:30.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真的希望有困難的人們吃這玩意兒\N{\fs38}Do you really want needy people to eat that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.00,0:15:34.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道 這看起來有點奇怪\N{\fs38}I don't know. This seems a little strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.28,0:15:36.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的 神父 我懂的\N{\fs38}Oh, all right, padre. I know the dance.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.56,0:15:39.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一百美元的捐助可以了結這事嗎\N{\fs38}Would a $100 donation make it right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.26,0:15:42.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩百\N{\fs38}200?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.44,0:15:45.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 我們可以捐三百  - 我們\N{\fs38}- We'll make it 3. - "We"?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.48,0:15:47.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 你們非常的慷慨  - 是的\N{\fs38}- That's very generous. - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.28,0:15:50.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 但我還要拿走那罐玉米\N{\fs38}Fine, but I'm gonna take that corn too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.62,0:15:56.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 好像有股穿堂風  - 我不知道 我沒感覺到\N{\fs38}- Is there a draft in here? - I-I don't know. I don't feel one.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.62,0:16:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你身上穿著這么件冬大衣當然暖著了\N{\fs38}Well, you're probably kept warm by that extra winter coat.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.12,0:16:03.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 嘿 好香啊  - 終于回來了 你們出去很長時間了\N{\fs38}- Hey, smells good. - Finally. That was a long walk.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.96,0:16:05.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 我們出去的時候覺得\N{\fs38}Yeah, while we were out, we just thought
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.10,0:16:06.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們應該順便看下新藝術派門\N{\fs38}we'd check out some Art Nouveau doors too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.70,0:16:08.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 我們正準備開動了\N{\fs38}Well, we're just about to eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.51,0:16:11.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mikey 你和Ian可以把桌子挪到客廳去嗎\N{\fs38}Mikey, can you and Ian move the table into the living room?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.80,0:16:12.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得這兒有股穿堂風\N{\fs38}I'm feeling a draft.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.98,0:16:14.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 屋里有穿堂風  - 我不知道 Mike\N{\fs38}- We have a draft? - I don't know, Mike.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.34,0:16:15.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經沒法分辨了 這一整天都\N{\fs38}I can't even tell anymore. This entire day has been...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.90,0:16:16.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- Annie  - 我得過去了\N{\fs38}- Annie! - I have to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.18,0:16:21.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 我們搬桌子吧  - 當然\N{\fs38}- Let's move the table. - Absolutely.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.20,0:16:23.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們不覺得應該先把盤子撤走嗎\N{\fs38}Whoa, don't you at least want to take the dishes off first?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.72,0:16:26.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們又不是在法國 我們可是男人\N{\fs38}Maybe if we were in France, but we're men.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.20,0:16:29.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 沒錯 - 法國也有男人\N{\fs38}- Yes! - They have men in France, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.22,0:16:30.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 爺爺 我來吧\N{\fs38}Okay, Grandpa, I'm taking over.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.02,0:16:32.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放尊重點 我們在抬桌子呢\N{\fs38}Hey, show some respect. We're lifting a table,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.00,0:16:34.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們不是在做凱格爾健肌運動 娘炮\N{\fs38}we're not doing kegel exercises, muffy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.00,0:16:34.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fs36}鍛煉男性盆底肌的運動 在基佬中風靡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.58,0:16:35.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又這樣\N{\fs38}More of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.32,0:16:37.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這個家里當個男女平等主義者真難 挪過去一點\N{\fs38}It is so hard to be a feminist in this family. Move over.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.88,0:16:40.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 自己找張桌子搬去  - 各位 你們要把我逼到沙發里了\N{\fs38}- Get your own table. - Guys, you're pushing me into the couch.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.34,0:16:43.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- Steve 你們在干什么  - 從上面跨過去\N{\fs38}- Steve, what are you doing? - Going over the top.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.23,0:16:46.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 爺爺放手  - 我在沙發上了 兩位 我在沙發上了\N{\fs38}- Grandpa, let go! - I'm on the sofa, guys. I'm on the sofa.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.64,0:16:54.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 這下盤子都撤走了\N{\fs38}Well, the plates are off the table.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.26,0:16:55.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ian 你什么毛病啊\N{\fs38}Ian, what's wrong with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.34,0:16:57.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我什么毛病 爺爺玩橄欖球的時候都站不穩了\N{\fs38}What's wrong with me? Grandpa keeled over playing football,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.65,0:16:59.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還讓他搬桌子\N{\fs38}you're trying to make him move a table?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.08,0:17:01.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 站不穩  - 橄欖球\N{\fs38}- Keeled over? - Football?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.94,0:17:03.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說"蔓"  你說"越莓"\N{\fs38}When I say "Cran," You say "Berry!"
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.76,0:17:04.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 蔓  - 哦\N{\fs38}- Cran... - Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.00,0:17:06.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,討厭 Eve 我們練習過的\N{\fs38}Damn it, Eve. We rehearsed this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.68,0:17:09.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,越莓\N{\fs38}Berry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.04,0:17:14.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們可以用這個肉汁盤乘東西吃\N{\fs38}We could all eat out of this gravy boat.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.14,0:17:17.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你玩橄欖球已經夠糟了\N{\fs38}It's bad enough you played football,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.48,0:17:19.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還想瞞著不說\N{\fs38}but you tried to keep it a secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.36,0:17:21.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有些人沒想瞞著 比如Ian\N{\fs38}Some of us didn't try very hard... Ian.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.70,0:17:23.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提醒我別跟那小子去拉斯維加斯\N{\fs38}Remind me not to go to Vegas with that guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.70,0:17:23.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fs36}著名賭城 許多人在那留下"不可說的秘密" 有句俗語叫"what happens in Vegas stays in Vegas"
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.90,0:17:25.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道的 Steve\N{\fs38}You know, Steve,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.33,0:17:28.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你手術以后應該凡事放緩一些\N{\fs38}you're supposed to take it easy after the surgery.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.10,0:17:32.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么 手術 什么手術 什么\N{\fs38}What? Surgery? What surgery? What...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.54,0:17:37.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 只是做了個腹腔鏡檢查  - 是 在你心臟里的\N{\fs38}- Just a little laparoscopic thing. - Yeah, in your heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.60,0:17:40.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧 你快去躺躺吧\N{\fs38}Come on. It's time for you to lie down.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.62,0:17:49.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以即使你父親心臟狀況不好\N{\fs38}So you snuck out and played football,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.18,0:17:52.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還是偷溜出去玩了橄欖球\N{\fs38}even though your father has a heart condition.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.42,0:17:53.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要辯解一句\N{\fs38}In my defense,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.34,0:17:56.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玩之前我都不知道他有心臟病\N{\fs38}I didn't know about the heart condition until after the football.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.58,0:17:59.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 那你是什么時候打算搬\N{\fs38}Okay, at which point you decided to move the heaviest
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.66,0:18:00.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們家最重的家具的\N{\fs38}piece of furniture we own?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.02,0:18:02.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,親愛的 那個瓷器櫥不賴\N{\fs38}That China cabinet's no slouch, honey.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.04,0:18:05.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- Mike  - 他是我爸爸\N{\fs38}- Mike. - He's my Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.70,0:18:07.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他從沒嬌慣過我\N{\fs38}He never coddled me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.97,0:18:09.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想他也不希望我嬌慣他\N{\fs38}And I don't think he wants me to coddle him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.61,0:18:11.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們只是對對方要求高\N{\fs38}We just expect the best from each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.48,0:18:14.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是個70歲的老人了 Mike\N{\fs38}He's a 70-year-old man, Mike.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.15,0:18:18.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高期望和忽略現實是有區別的\N{\fs38}There's a difference between high expectations and ignoring reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.10,0:18:25.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泳裝版 我不確定你的心臟起搏器受不受得了\N{\fs38}Swimsuit edition? Not sure that's good for your ticker.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.58,0:18:26.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鬼靈精\N{\fs38}Smartass.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.68,0:18:34.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老爸 當我被確診時\N{\fs38}You know, Dad, when I was diagnosed,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.92,0:18:38.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很多人對待我的態度都不一樣了 但你從沒有\N{\fs38}a lot of people treated me differently, but you never did.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.72,0:18:40.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想看輕你\N{\fs38}I didn't wanna underestimate you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.80,0:18:42.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道 我很感激\N{\fs38}I know, and I appreciate that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.72,0:18:47.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以在公園 你有突發狀況時\N{\fs38}So when you had your, uh, thing in the park,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.48,0:18:50.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想用相同的方式對待你\N{\fs38}I wanted to do the same for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.38,0:18:52.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但事實是\N{\fs38}But the truth is,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.18,0:18:53.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看輕某人與向現實妥協\N{\fs38}there's a difference between underestimating someone
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.94,0:18:56.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并不是一回事\N{\fs38}and coming to terms with reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.16,0:19:00.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 我的心絞痛沒什么大不了  - 問題可大了\N{\fs38}- My heart twinge was nothing. - No, it was "Not" Nothing,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.46,0:19:04.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像我這個也不是因為喝了太多咖啡的關系\N{\fs38}any more than this... is from too much coffee.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.46,0:19:04.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fs36}帕金森的病因是中樞抑制遞質減少 引起中樞神經興奮
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.22,0:19:09.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽著\N{\fs38}Look.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.60,0:19:14.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是我的孩子\N{\fs38}You're my boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.36,0:19:18.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是很懊惱\N{\fs38}And I just hate that...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.01,0:19:25.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們曾經那么擅長打橄欖球\N{\fs38}we used to be so good at football.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.66,0:19:27.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道\N{\fs38}I know...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.56,0:19:31.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現實是很糟\N{\fs38}and it sucks.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.31,0:19:35.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但說出來沒有關系的\N{\fs38}But it's okay to say that out loud.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.94,0:19:39.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有 值得安慰的是\N{\fs38}And hey, we can take solace in the fact that
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.94,0:19:41.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們依然比Ian厲害\N{\fs38}we're both still better than Ian.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.50,0:19:45.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為他實在是太爛了\N{\fs38}'Cause he sucks!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.16,0:19:46.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每個家庭都有它自己的戰術手冊\N{\fs38}Every family has its own playbook.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.00,0:19:49.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有些戰術用了一次又一次\N{\fs38}Some plays get run over and over again.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.42,0:19:53.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 危機解除了\N{\fs38}Okay. Crisis averted.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.08,0:19:56.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天我們來整理你的衣柜\N{\fs38}Tomorrow we reorganize your closets.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.48,0:19:59.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 哦 媽媽 她不行  - 我不行\N{\fs38}- Oh, Mom, she can't. - I can't?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.02,0:20:01.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不\N{\fs38}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.64,0:20:04.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 為什么不行  - 你要載我去機場啊 記得嗎\N{\fs38}- Why not? - You're taking me to the airport, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.46,0:20:06.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一整天呢 我臨時買了張機票\N{\fs38}All day. I bought a last-minute ticket,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.55,0:20:08.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以得從波士頓起飛\N{\fs38}so now I have to fly out of Boston.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.42,0:20:11.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,波士頓 Leigh 說真的\N{\fs38}Boston? Leigh, honestly.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.38,0:20:14.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我早跟你說過 你得提前幾個月訂\N{\fs38}I told you, you have to book months in advance.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.52,0:20:18.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 謝謝  - 你把我寄給你的日歷弄丟了嗎\N{\fs38}- Thank you. - Did you lose that calendar I sent you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.07,0:20:20.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上面有每日一詞呢\N{\fs38}'Cause there's a word-a-day in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.22,0:20:21.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們把我們最喜歡的戰術稱作 傳統\N{\fs38}The plays we like the most, we call traditions.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.10,0:20:24.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝了 Harris 這對我來說意義重大\N{\fs38}Thanks, Harris. This really means a lot to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.17,0:20:28.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 哦 那是什么  - 家庭版蔓越莓醬\N{\fs38}- Oh, what's that? - My homemade cranberry sauce.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.01,0:20:32.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些是丁香嗎 聞起來好棒啊\N{\fs38}Are those cloves? It smells amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.38,0:20:37.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下 什么 你認真的\N{\fs38}Wait a minute. What? Are you serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.92,0:20:40.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但最后 你總會遭遇一些新情況\N{\fs38}But eventually, you come up against a new situation.
